## Data & Storage
- ✅ Connect to a database for data persistence and multi device support
- ✅ Data backup & restore — export/import all data as JSON
- ✅ CSV/JSON import — bring in data from other time tracking tools

## Time Tracking
- ✅ Reminders — browser notifications to clock out if you forgot, or to clock in at a set time
- ✅ Add a clock in / clock out feature with time rounding
- ✅ Add option for coarse or fine time rounding with 1 min, 5 min, 15 min, and 30 min options
- ✅ Duplicate entry — copy a past session to today with one click

## Projects & Billing
- ✅ Add projects and clients for managing multiple projects and clients
- ✅ Billable vs non-billable flag per entry, with totals separated in exports and earnings
- ✅ Invoice generation — produce a printable/PDF invoice from a month or project's hours
- Multi-currency support for the hourly rate

## Goals & Insights
- ✅ Target hours — set a daily or weekly goal and show a progress bar / how many hours remain
- ✅ Calendar heatmap view — visualize days worked at a glance, spot gaps

## UI & Experience
